DISCIPLINARY DOCKET

92-422. Columbus Bar Assn. v. Gaba.

This matter came on for further consideration upon the filing on September 22, 2000, by respondent, Lawrence Charles Gaba, of a motion to purge contempt. Upon consideration thereof,

IT IS ORDERED by this court that the motion be, and hereby is, granted, and that respondent is purged of contempt in this matter.
